Package: pidgin-hide-chat
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pidgin Hide Chat on Join
 This plugin adds an entry in the context menu of every channel you have in your buddy list to allow you to hide the chat window when you join the channel. (This is usefull when you have a huge amount of channels in your buddy list and don't want to have all of these poping up each time you start Pidgin.)

Package: pidgin-hide-chat-dbg
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: pidgin-hide-chat, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pidgin Hide Chat on Join Debug Symbols
 Debug symbols for the Pidgin Hide Chat on Join plugin

